rows.label: qst201006_0010
rows.name:
Driving us into a corner, eh? I've gotta
admit, I'm impressed.

rows.label: qst201006_0020
rows.name:
Come on, Seori! Mikumari! Try a little
harder, won't you?!

rows.label: qst201006_0030
rows.name:
You were born to fight, weren't you?
So act like you mean it!

rows.label: qst201006_0050
rows.name: I'll set them up for you. Move on my signal.

rows.label: qst201006_0120
rows.name:
What's the meaning of this?
Has her Driver succumbed?

rows.label: qst201006_0130
rows.name: Damn. They demolished the support squad?

rows.label: qst201006_0140
rows.name:
Guess the plan to keep her Driver at a distance
backfired. Can't anyone do their bloody job right?!

rows.label: qst201006_0170
rows.name:
We can't just stick around, can we?
Shut your trap and do as I say!

rows.label: qst201006_0190
rows.name:
Forget about that good-for-nothing!
Just hurry up and come with me!
